OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAll
OL,6,Fparts remaining dry and settled into
OL,7,Fthe weekend with plenty of warm
OL,8,Fsunshine. Patchy overnight low cloud
OL,9,Fin the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
